d the world. Factories present their products, capabilities, and certifications, while buyers search, compare, and connect directly — all in one trusted plat...'.","relatedInformation":[{"file":"./lib/i18n/locales/en.ts","start":8593,"length":329,"messageText":"The expected type comes from property 'desc' which is declared here on type '{ readonly title: \"What is SourceNest?\"; readonly desc: \"SourceNest is a premium global digital marketplace where importers, buyers, and sourcing professionals discover reviewed manufacturers and factories from around the world. Factories present their products, capabilities, and certifications, while buyers search,...'","category":3,"code":6500}]},{"start":7923,"length":9,"code":2322,"category":1,"messageText":"Type '\"للمشترين والمستوردين\"' is not assignable to type '\"For Buyers & Importers\"'.","relatedInformation":[{"file":"./lib/i18n/locales/en.ts","start":8930,"length":35,"messageText":"The expected type comes from property 'forBuyers' which is declared here on type '{ readonly title: \"What is SourceNest?\"; readonly desc: \"SourceNest is a premium global digital marketplace where importers, buyers, and sourcing professionals discover reviewed manufacturers and factories from around the world. Factories present their products, capabilities, and certifications, while buyers search,...'","category":3,"code":6500}]},{"start":7964,"length":13,"code":2322,"category":1,"messageText":"Type '\"اكتشف المصنعين الموثوقين، وقارن بين الموردين جنباً إلى جنب، واحفظ المفضلات، وأرسل طلبات عروض الأسعار، وتواصل مباشرة مع المصانع. كل سير عمل المصادر الخاص بك في مكان واحد - مجاناً تماماً.\"' is not assignable to type '\"Discover reviewed manufacturers, compare suppliers side-by-side, save favorites, send quote requests, and communicate directly with factories. Your entire sourcing workflow in one place — completely free.\"'.","relatedInformation":[{"file":"./lib/i18n/locales/en.ts","start":8973,"length":221,"messageText":"The expected type co